snippet.title: Paper Nebula - Announcement Trailer - Roguelike Arcade Game
snippet.description:
Paper Nebula is a fast paced, arcade style scroller, reinvented as a Roguelike! This space shooter will have you blasting through endless waves of alien ships, to escape the Paper Nebula. With adorable paper style graphics and intense gameplay, you wouldn't want to be trapped anywhere else.

Wishlist on Steam now https://store.steampowered.com/app/2062100/

Find out more at
https://www.PaperNebula.com
